title: [Zul Logoth, Moss Tunnel]
description: Lacy, phosphorescent moss clings tightly to the small stalactites lining the tunnel, but some of the heavier clusters dangle like banners in the air.  The path has been unnaturally widened, allowing ample room for carts to transport supplies along the route.
location: the tunnels and caverns of Zul Logoth
